653
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:19,510
And since then,

654
00:35:20,030 --> 00:35:21,800
no one would come to protect us anymore.

655
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,070
So,

656
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:25,070
those who could leave, left.

657
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:27,030
