702
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:46,150
I suspect he used some method

703
00:36:46,190 --> 00:36:47,400
to block the artifact's detection.

704
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:48,670
Your father

705
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,190
